name: fast-check-benchmarks
description: Various benchmarks around fast-check: mostly to measure improvements of the lib itself

scripts.profile: node --prof --no-logfile-per-isolate --trace-deopt --trace-opt-verbose profile.js > deopt.out && node --prof-process v8.log > v8.out
scripts.profile:deep: node --prof --no-logfile-per-isolate --trace-deopt --trace-opt-verbose --code-comments --print-opt-code profile.js > deopt.out && node --prof-process v8.log > v8.out
